 This program includes cost for a Software Integration Lab (SIL) stand up as the depot source of repair (DSOR) states BU 8.1 software maintenance will be performed organically at WR-ALC.

 This funding request will support removal of the Dynamic Re-tasking Capability (DRC) on those aircraft modified with DRC during the Gulf War, during the install of Block 8.1.

 Milestone/Development Status

 Successful full rate production decision 1 Oct 2019.

 BU 8.1 operational testing occurred 9 Jul 2018 to 28 Sep 2018 with no reported CAT 1 deficiencies, formal out brief provided to AMC 22 Jul 2019.

 An adversarial assessment was performed second quarter FY 2019; no new risks were identified. Full rate production decision approval - 1 Oct 2019.

 RAA milestone was achieved in 28 June 2022.
