Note: Totals in this Exhibit P-40 set may not be exact or sum exactly due to rounding.

 Justification:
 This program, P-3A Mod 8738, HC-Communications Modernization Phase II, is a new start.
 This program, P-3A Mod 8769, MC-EO/IR Sensor Modification, is a new start.

 Primary efforts in FY 2027 include: MC-Airborne Mission Networking (AbMN), MC/AC-Communications Modernization Phase I, MC-Trainer Modifications, MC-Star XIII and MC-EO/IR Sensor Modification.




