 improve readiness and operational reach of existing force structure, and deliver resilient Infrastructure, equipment, and personnel.

 The Mobile User Objective System (MUOS) provides a worldwide, multi-service population of mobile and fixed-site terminal users with ultra-high frequency (UHF), narrowband, and beyond line-of-sight satellite
