 - Runway Snow Removal and Cleaning Equipment Vehicles includes front mounted brooms, multi-purpose blowers, and plows.
 - Base Maintenance Support Vehicles includes loaders, dozers, back hoes, water distribution trucks and heavy construction equipment.

 This requirement supports performance of a full financial audit as required by title 10 U.S.C. Chapter 9A, Sec 240-D.

 Funding for this exhibit contained in PE 0702831SF.

 This program falls within the Enterprise Management & Information Technology mission area. Enterprise Management provides the personnel and infrastructure required to manage USSF headquarters
 functions at the service and field command levels, including the Space Service Acquisition Executive for Space Systems and Programs, Office of the Assistant Secretary for Space Acquisition and Integration, the
 Office of the Chief of Space Operations (OCSO), the Space Staff, and Secretariat. Information Technology includes the IT infrastructure required for the USSF to acquire, sustain, and operate its assets. Space
 Force investment program interdependencies include:



