 The Defense Enterprise Accounting & Management System (DEAMS) is compliant with the Clinger-Cohen Act and the DoD's Business Enterprise Architecture (BEA). This requirement supports performance of a
 full financial audit as required by title 10 U.S.C. Chapter 9A, Sec 240-D.



